pg-hardstorage (0.1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging for the v0.1.1 cheap-closure release.
  * Three binary packages: pg-hardstorage (agent + CLI),
    pg-hardstorage-common (shared data), pg-hardstorage-server
    (stub for the v0.5 control plane).
  * Ships systemd units, sysusers / tmpfiles fragments, bash
    completion, and manpages.

